                        , others somewhat varying in the difference of the greatest declination, making it when it is least (as in our time) not lesse then 23, 30, and in the Periodicall restitution thereof.
                     But to speake freely, I cannot so easily bee drawne into this opinion, but rather thinke the greatest declination of the Sunne, to be 
